WEBVTT

1
00:02:28.160 --> 00:02:30.060
Up! Up!

2
00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:42.060
Hurry!

3
00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:50.060
Don't push!

4
00:02:55.160 --> 00:02:57.060
Hurry!

5
00:03:05.160 --> 00:03:07.060
Up the tree. quickly!

6
00:03:10.160 --> 00:03:14.060
Pull him down quickly. quickly!

7
00:03:16.160 --> 00:03:18.060
Catch the flag.

8
00:03:19.160 --> 00:03:21.060
Wait.

9
00:03:30.160 --> 00:03:32.060
Don't let him get down

10
00:03:45.160 --> 00:03:47.060
Hurry!

11
00:04:03.160 --> 00:04:05.060
Careful!

12
00:04:30.160 --> 00:04:32.060
Calm down! The winner this year...

13
00:04:33.160 --> 00:04:37.060
is Ai Bak Tim

14
00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:50.160
Sawadee everyone...

15
00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:52.160
from Ban Nong Pradoo.

16
00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:54.160
We are gathering for good merit
at this festival.

17
00:04:54.160 --> 00:04:58.160
to give robes to the monks.
and Ong Bak.

18
00:04:58.160 --> 00:05:02.160
who is the protective icon
for the well-being of our village.

19
00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:04.160
This festival...

20
00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:06.160
is to remind us that...

21
00:05:06.160 --> 00:05:08.160
in 7 days we will be...

22
00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:10.460
celebrating Ong Bak.

23
00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:13.160
The last time...

24
00:05:13.160 --> 00:05:17.060
being 24 years ago.

25
00:05:18.160 --> 00:05:20.160
This means...

26
00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:24.060
all prosperity will return
to us once more.

27
00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:36.060
Where is the amulet?

28
00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:43.160
It's not good.

29
00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:45.160
There is a little damage -

30
00:05:45.160 --> 00:05:47.160
Not quite perfect.

31
00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:50.160
200.000 baht for this is not cheap.

32
00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:54.060
Why don't you want to sell it?

33
00:05:55.160 --> 00:05:58.160
Ow! How much do you want?

34
00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:01.160
Don. I'm not selling.

35
00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:04.160
Ow! Why do you change your mind?

36
00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:07.160
I came a long way
from Bangkok just for this.

37
00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:09.160
I've never given you any promise...

38
00:06:09.160 --> 00:06:11.160
to sell it to you.

39
00:06:11.160 --> 00:06:13.160
I want to give this to my son.
Bak Hum Lae.

40
00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:17.060
the day he's ordained here
as a monk. for Ong Bak.

41
00:06:19.160 --> 00:06:23.160
Call me whenever you want to sell it.

42
00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:26.160
No. no. I don't have a telephone.

43
00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:28.160
I'll give you my address.

44
00:06:28.160 --> 00:06:30.160
so whenever you want to sell.

45
00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:32.060
you can write to me.

46
00:06:43.160 --> 00:06:45.160
Is this good enough. grandma?

47
00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:48.160
I made it for Ai Tim
for his ordination.

48
00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:50.160
It's good.

49
00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:53.160
Where did Ai Tim come from.

50
00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:55.160
and how come he grew up
in the temple?

51
00:06:55.160 --> 00:06:57.160
He's now a man.

52
00:06:57.160 --> 00:07:01.160
Ai Tim is an ophan.

53
00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:03.160
He was left at the temple by someone...

54
00:07:03.160 --> 00:07:05.160
when he was a baby.

55
00:07:05.160 --> 00:07:08.160
Pra Kroo (the Abbot) took pity on him.

56
00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:10.060
and adopted him.

57
00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:13.160
And everyone says...

58
00:07:13.160 --> 00:07:17.060
he has grown up well under Ong Bak.

59
00:07:24.260 --> 00:07:26.260
Hitting the earth!

60
00:07:26.260 --> 00:07:28.160
Crocodile whipping tail!

61
00:07:29.260 --> 00:07:31.260
Confronting elephant!

62
00:07:31.260 --> 00:07:32.260
Hanuman (Monkey) giving ring.

63
00:07:32.260 --> 00:07:34.260
The threatening fight.

64
00:07:34.260 --> 00:07:35.260
The rear kick.

65
00:07:35.260 --> 00:07:37.260
Both elbows attacking...

66
00:07:37.260 --> 00:07:38.260
followed with high knee.

67
00:07:38.260 --> 00:07:40.260
Raising the army.

68
00:07:40.260 --> 00:07:42.260
Getting high strength.

69
00:07:42.260 --> 00:07:44.260
Cutting through the enemy.

70
00:07:44.260 --> 00:07:46.260
Avoiding danger.

71
00:07:46.260 --> 00:07:48.260
Putting your head down.

72
00:07:48.260 --> 00:07:50.260
Knight throwing an axe.

73
00:07:50.260 --> 00:07:52.260
Wave smashing the shore.

74
00:07:52.260 --> 00:07:54.160
Meet friend. join friend.

75
00:07:55.260 --> 00:07:57.260
Knight catching monkeys.

76
00:07:57.260 --> 00:07:59.160
Breaking the joins.

77
00:08:00.260 --> 00:08:02.260
Snake chasing lizard.

78
00:08:02.260 --> 00:08:04.260
Cliff shaking.

79
00:08:04.260 --> 00:08:06.260
Sticky water.

80
00:08:06.260 --> 00:08:07.260
Throwing the spear.

81
00:08:07.260 --> 00:08:09.260
Breaking the sword.

82
00:08:09.260 --> 00:08:10.260
Raising the body.

83
00:08:10.260 --> 00:08:12.160
Horse replacing bird.

84
00:08:25.260 --> 00:08:27.260
I'll teach you all these styles...

85
00:08:27.260 --> 00:08:31.160
but I forbid you
to use them for money.

86
00:08:32.260 --> 00:08:36.260
Do you understand. Bak Tim?

87
00:08:36.260 --> 00:08:38.260
I understand. Pra Kroo.

88
00:08:38.260 --> 00:08:40.160
Good.

89
00:08:47.260 --> 00:08:49.260
He has gone.

90
00:08:49.260 --> 00:08:53.160
You said you understood. Really?

91
00:09:02.260 --> 00:09:04.260
There is a story that...

92
00:09:04.260 --> 00:09:07.260
Pra Kroo learnt this boxing...

93
00:09:07.260 --> 00:09:11.260
from the ancient books.

94
00:09:11.260 --> 00:09:14.260
Then Pra Kroo wanted a challenge.

95
00:09:14.260 --> 00:09:17.260
He went into the boxing ring
for money...

96
00:09:17.260 --> 00:09:21.160
and he hit his opponent to death.

97
00:09:22.260 --> 00:09:25.260
He felt very guilty.

98
00:09:25.260 --> 00:09:27.260
so he became a monk.

99
00:09:27.260 --> 00:09:29.160
Thai boxing is very dangerous.

100
00:09:30.260 --> 00:09:34.160
I don't want you to use it. unless
it is absolutely necessary.

101
00:09:35.260 --> 00:09:37.160
Understand?

102
00:09:38.260 --> 00:09:42.160
Or are you still not clear?

103
00:09:43.260 --> 00:09:46.260
Come. fight with me.

104
00:09:46.260 --> 00:09:47.260
Ai Bak. here.

105
00:09:47.260 --> 00:09:49.160
Uncle!
Come on!

106
00:10:24.260 --> 00:10:28.160
Who is there? What are you doing?

107
00:10:37.260 --> 00:10:39.160
Hurry!

108
00:10:49.260 --> 00:10:50.260
Bak Don...

109
00:10:50.260 --> 00:10:54.160
is the one
that cut off the head of Ong Bak.

110
00:10:58.260 --> 00:11:02.260
He took all the donation money too.
Pra Kroo.

111
00:11:02.260 --> 00:11:06.160
Bak Don! Evil son!

112
00:11:08.260 --> 00:11:11.260
If Pra Ong Bak has no head.

113
00:11:11.260 --> 00:11:15.260
our village will be faced
with disaster.

114
00:11:15.260 --> 00:11:17.260
Calm down. calm down!

115
00:11:17.260 --> 00:11:21.260
We must try
to get Ong Bak's head back...

116
00:11:21.260 --> 00:11:25.260
to our village before the ceremony day.

117
00:11:25.260 --> 00:11:29.160
Where can we find it. Pra Kroo ?

118
00:11:31.260 --> 00:11:34.260
I will bring Ong Bak back here myself.

119
00:11:34.260 --> 00:11:38.160
Who knows where Bak Don is?

120
00:11:40.260 --> 00:11:44.260
The hopes of the people
of Ban Nong Pradoo Sukon...

121
00:11:44.260 --> 00:11:47.260
is in your hands.

122
00:11:47.260 --> 00:11:50.260
In this tube is a holy herbal medicine.

123
00:11:50.260 --> 00:11:52.260
My teacher told me...

124
00:11:52.260 --> 00:11:55.260
it belonged to Kroo Dum.

125
00:11:55.260 --> 00:11:57.160
Keep it with you.

126
00:12:03.260 --> 00:12:05.160
This is the address of Bak Don.

127
00:12:06.260 --> 00:12:10.260
and this is a letter to Bak Hum Lae.

128
00:12:10.260 --> 00:12:14.160
Tim. you must return with Ong Bak...

129
00:12:15.260 --> 00:12:17.160
to our village.

130
00:12:26.260 --> 00:12:30.160
This is the money for your journey.

131
00:12:31.260 --> 00:12:33.160
All my hopes are with you.

132
00:12:36.260 --> 00:12:40.160
My mum gave me this ring
before she died.

133
00:12:41.260 --> 00:12:45.160
Warn. please look after grandma.

134
00:13:02.260 --> 00:13:06.160
We've all contributed together...

135
00:13:07.260 --> 00:13:11.160
for the fares.

136
00:13:46.260 --> 00:13:48.160
He's losing.

137
00:13:58.260 --> 00:14:02.260
Hey! What bike you using to race?

138
00:14:02.260 --> 00:14:04.260
Why did you lose so easily like this?

139
00:14:04.260 --> 00:14:06.260
Hey! Why are you speaking that way?

140
00:14:06.260 --> 00:14:08.260
Win or lose is normal in any bet.

141
00:14:08.260 --> 00:14:10.260
It isn't fair to blame me.

142
00:14:10.260 --> 00:14:13.260
Why did you use a woman
to race with me?

143
00:14:13.260 --> 00:14:15.260
Why not?
What's wrong with being a woman?

144
00:14:15.260 --> 00:14:18.260
Ow! You dare race against me!

145
00:14:18.260 --> 00:14:19.260
You cow!

146
00:14:19.260 --> 00:14:22.260
If you rode as fast as your mouth.
you'd probably win!

147
00:14:22.260 --> 00:14:24.160
Hey! Hey!

148
00:14:38.260 --> 00:14:40.260
Hey! Why don't you pay me in cash?

149
00:14:40.260 --> 00:14:43.260
You bet me with drugs. didn't you?

150
00:14:43.260 --> 00:14:47.160
You told me it was OK
to use drugs instead of cash.

151
00:14:48.260 --> 00:14:50.160
OK

152
00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:59.360
I'll give you only 10.000.

153
00:14:59.360 --> 00:15:02.360
after deducting the 10.000
you own me.

154
00:15:02.360 --> 00:15:04.360
I pay you interest every month.

155
00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:05.360
and the loan is not yet due.

156
00:15:05.360 --> 00:15:07.360
Can't you give me all the money now?

157
00:15:07.360 --> 00:15:09.360
Do you want it or not?

158
00:15:09.360 --> 00:15:13.260
OK . Better than nothing.

159
00:15:20.360 --> 00:15:23.360
Hey! Give me all of that.

160
00:15:23.360 --> 00:15:25.360
What!

161
00:15:25.360 --> 00:15:27.260
Give me!

162
00:15:28.360 --> 00:15:30.360
You've already got my money.

163
00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:33.360
Can't you give a few tablets
to my friends?

164
00:15:33.360 --> 00:15:36.360
You can find this drug anywhere -

165
00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:38.360
you don't have to take mine.

166
00:15:38.360 --> 00:15:40.360
Better not to use my drugs.

167
00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:43.360
They're too strong.
Your friends may go into shock.

168
00:15:43.360 --> 00:15:45.360
Believe me.

169
00:15:45.360 --> 00:15:47.260
Huh?

170
00:15:58.360 --> 00:16:00.260
Son of a bitch!

171
00:16:08.360 --> 00:16:12.360
Eh! You're back at last. My money!

172
00:16:12.360 --> 00:16:16.360
Give me my share quickly. Quickly!

173
00:16:16.360 --> 00:16:18.360
Ai Keng caught me.

174
00:16:18.360 --> 00:16:21.360
He knew we bet with fake drugs.
He took all the money back

175
00:16:21.360 --> 00:16:23.360
What? Don't tease me -

176
00:16:23.360 --> 00:16:25.360
not funny at all.

177
00:16:25.360 --> 00:16:27.360
Muey. look at my face.

178
00:16:27.360 --> 00:16:28.860
Do you think I kicked myself?

179
00:16:29.360 --> 00:16:30.360
Damn!

180
00:16:33.360 --> 00:16:37.360
Oy! Why are you poking me?
I'm still in pain.

181
00:16:37.360 --> 00:16:39.860
Oh well. How come you got caught?

182
00:16:40.360 --> 00:16:41.360
Forget it!

183
00:16:41.360 --> 00:16:42.860
Do you have 200 baht?

184
00:16:43.360 --> 00:16:46.360
What! Lost all my share
and still asking me for my money?

185
00:16:46.360 --> 00:16:48.360
Listen! Muey.

186
00:16:48.360 --> 00:16:51.360
When I won. you took the money.

187
00:16:51.360 --> 00:16:53.360
Now I've lost.
so you must share the loss too.

188
00:16:53.360 --> 00:16:56.360
Ow! You're stupid to get caught.

189
00:16:56.360 --> 00:16:58.360
and lose the money in your hands.

190
00:16:58.360 --> 00:17:00.360
So I'm stupid and you're clever!

191
00:17:00.360 --> 00:17:03.360
Ai Keng give me only 3 days.

192
00:17:03.360 --> 00:17:07.360
If I don't pay back his loan
he'll hit me. Hit me!

193
00:17:07.360 --> 00:17:09.260
Ai Hum Lae?

194
00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:13.360
Is it really you. Ai Hum Lae?

195
00:17:13.360 --> 00:17:14.360
Hi.

196
00:17:14.360 --> 00:17:17.860
Er... Muay. is he your friend?
Your friend?

197
00:17:17.860 --> 00:17:19.360
How could he be my friend?

198
00:17:19.360 --> 00:17:22.360
He is calling you. isn't he?

199
00:17:22.360 --> 00:17:24.360
Do you know him?
Yeah!

200
00:17:24.360 --> 00:17:27.360
Remember me? I'm Bak Tim
from Ban Nong Pradoo.

201
00:17:27.360 --> 00:17:29.360
Hey! Fool! I don't know you.

202
00:17:29.360 --> 00:17:33.360
Fool! Understand! I've just told you
I don't know you!

203
00:17:33.860 --> 00:17:35.360
But I know you. Ai Hum Lae

204
00:17:35.360 --> 00:17:37.360
Hum Lae. Hum what!

205
00:17:37.360 --> 00:17:39.360
What a stupid name! Hum Lae!

206
00:17:39.360 --> 00:17:41.360
Bad luck! I warn you...you're fool

207
00:17:41.360 --> 00:17:44.360
Ow! No need to lie!
Ai Hum Lae... Oops

208
00:17:44.360 --> 00:17:46.360
Sorry! Slip of my tongue.

209
00:17:46.360 --> 00:17:49.360
Mind your own business.

210
00:17:49.360 --> 00:17:52.360
Get out of my sight! Out!

211
00:17:52.360 --> 00:17:55.360
OK. You said you were from...
Ban? Which?

212
00:17:55.360 --> 00:17:56.360
Ban Nong Pradoo.

213
00:17:56.360 --> 00:17:58.260
That's it. Ban Nong Pradoo.

214
00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:01.360
OK. I'm leaving.

215
00:18:01.360 --> 00:18:03.360
So you're both from Ban Nong Pradoo.
Can have a good chat!

216
00:18:03.360 --> 00:18:05.360
Very funny! You've made your point!

217
00:18:05.360 --> 00:18:08.360
Go! Go away.
but give me the money first.

218
00:18:08.360 --> 00:18:10.260
Here! For your medicine.

219
00:18:11.360 --> 00:18:15.360
I'm going now. Ai Hum Lae

220
00:18:15.360 --> 00:18:19.360
Listen. peasant!
You should return to your hometown.

221
00:18:19.360 --> 00:18:20.260
Go!

222
00:18:21.360 --> 00:18:24.360
Ai Ham Lae.
I have to give you a letter.

223
00:18:24.360 --> 00:18:28.260
I told you I don't know you!
Get out!

224
00:18:32.360 --> 00:18:34.360
This is my place.

225
00:18:34.360 --> 00:18:37.360
Don't be angry with me.
Close the door.

226
00:18:37.360 --> 00:18:39.360
Don't let mosquitos in.

227
00:18:39.360 --> 00:18:43.260
I'm in a bad mood and depressed

228
00:18:44.360 --> 00:18:46.260
Ai Hum Lae.

229
00:18:47.360 --> 00:18:51.260
Our villagers are in serious trouble...

230
00:18:52.360 --> 00:18:55.360
because Bak Don
stole the head of Ong Bak

231
00:18:55.360 --> 00:18:59.360
The Chief sent me here to see you.

232
00:18:59.360 --> 00:19:02.360
so you can help me to find Ong Bak

233
00:19:02.360 --> 00:19:05.360
I have Bak Don's address.

234
00:19:05.360 --> 00:19:08.360
No need to talk yet.
and put your things down here

235
00:19:08.360 --> 00:19:09.360
You're better have a wash first.

236
00:19:09.360 --> 00:19:11.360
Go. go now.

237
00:19:11.360 --> 00:19:13.360
Here. here is the washroom.

238
00:19:13.360 --> 00:19:14.360
Go in.

239
00:19:14.360 --> 00:19:15.860
I don't have any other clothing.

240
00:19:15.860 --> 00:19:18.360
Don't worry I'll give you my towel.
Go in. go.

241
00:19:18.860 --> 00:19:20.360
I'll turn on the light for you.

242
00:19:20.360 --> 00:19:23.360
Soap is on your left.
toothbrush on your right.

243
00:19:23.360 --> 00:19:26.360
Mind the slippery floor.

244
00:19:26.360 --> 00:19:28.260
Hello! Muay!

245
00:19:29.360 --> 00:19:31.260
I'll meet you at the stadium -

246
00:19:32.360 --> 00:19:34.260
the boxing stadium. OK.

247
00:20:15.360 --> 00:20:17.360
Do you still accept the bet?

248
00:20:17.360 --> 00:20:19.360
Do I have time?

249
00:20:19.360 --> 00:20:21.260
Yes.

250
00:20:22.360 --> 00:20:24.260
Here! All of them!

251
00:20:36.360 --> 00:20:38.260
Do you have the amulet?

252
00:20:40.360 --> 00:20:42.360
The chief changed his mind
and didn't want to sell. Boss.

253
00:20:42.360 --> 00:20:45.360
But I have the head of Ong Bak. Boss.

254
00:20:45.360 --> 00:20:48.360
This is the most holy thing
in the village...

255
00:20:48.360 --> 00:20:52.260
that they all worship.
and the most valuable.

256
00:20:53.360 --> 00:20:56.360
This broken head -

257
00:20:56.360 --> 00:20:58.260
why did you bring it to me?

258
00:20:59.360 --> 00:21:03.360
I'm not interested. Take it away!

259
00:21:03.360 --> 00:21:06.360
My head is hurting enough without...

260
00:21:06.360 --> 00:21:10.260
you spoiling my mood.

261
00:21:15.360 --> 00:21:17.860
Today. Captain seems
to have little to please him.

262
00:21:18.360 --> 00:21:20.360
Look at your fighter. Pearl Harbour.

263
00:21:20.360 --> 00:21:23.860
I think he's losing to Arun. my fighter.
with his Kami Kaze technique.

264
00:21:23.860 --> 00:21:25.260
Defeat's certain!

265
00:21:59.360 --> 00:22:02.360
I don't have the money yet -
still trying to get some.

266
00:22:02.360 --> 00:22:06.360
I'm not asking for money.
I can find that myself.

267
00:22:06.360 --> 00:22:10.360
Now you're selling drugs too!

268
00:22:10.360 --> 00:22:11.360
Yes.

269
00:22:16.360 --> 00:22:18.860
My fighter will win
the next competition.

270
00:22:18.860 --> 00:22:22.360
If you think you will win.
then why not increase your bet.

271
00:22:22.360 --> 00:22:25.360
Any sum you like. ha ha!

272
00:22:25.360 --> 00:22:26.360
You need not preach to me.

273
00:22:26.460 --> 00:22:27.460
you don't really understand me.

274
00:22:27.460 --> 00:22:29.460
Just because of one stinking male...

275
00:22:29.460 --> 00:22:33.460
you turn yourself into this low-life.

276
00:22:33.460 --> 00:22:35.460
Muay! You're not my mum!

277
00:22:35.460 --> 00:22:39.460
Because we've no parents.
you've become this bad.

278
00:22:39.460 --> 00:22:43.360
Yes. a bad person like me.
who has brought you up until now.

279
00:22:43.460 --> 00:22:47.960
From now on. a good person like you
should leave me alone.

280
00:22:54.460 --> 00:22:58.360
Yes. tell me whenever you want it.

281
00:23:09.460 --> 00:23:11.360
Strike. strike.

282
00:23:12.460 --> 00:23:14.360
Knock out.

283
00:23:24.460 --> 00:23:26.360
Get up and hit back.

284
00:23:36.460 --> 00:23:38.360
Yesss...

285
00:23:40.460 --> 00:23:44.460
The next one is coming.

286
00:23:44.460 --> 00:23:47.460
Tell me if you still want to bet.

287
00:23:47.460 --> 00:23:49.360
(laughs)

288
00:23:51.460 --> 00:23:53.360
The winner is ... Pearl Harbour.

289
00:23:55.460 --> 00:23:57.460
Damn!

290
00:23:57.460 --> 00:23:59.360
Pearl Habour is the Number One.

291
00:24:01.460 --> 00:24:04.460
Two wins two minutes.
Two wins two minutes.

292
00:24:04.460 --> 00:24:06.460
Where are all my things?

293
00:24:06.460 --> 00:24:07.460
What?

294
00:24:07.460 --> 00:24:08.460
My money bag. where is it?

295
00:24:08.460 --> 00:24:10.460
I don't know. I didn't take it.

296
00:24:10.460 --> 00:24:12.360
Him.

297
00:24:17.460 --> 00:24:20.460
Two and one...

298
00:24:20.460 --> 00:24:22.360
Oh! A fresh challenger.

299
00:24:28.460 --> 00:24:32.360
Taking bets now. taking bets now.

300
00:24:35.460 --> 00:24:39.460
Aw... How come that peasant
is in the fighting ring?

301
00:24:39.460 --> 00:24:43.360
Yeh... Ai Tim is surely dead.

302
00:24:44.460 --> 00:24:47.460
I'll give you 10 to 1.

303
00:24:47.460 --> 00:24:50.460
But you'd better not dare to bet.

304
00:24:50.460 --> 00:24:54.360
OK. I'll bet one million.
if you'll dare to accept it.

305
00:24:55.460 --> 00:24:56.460
I accept.

306
00:24:56.960 --> 00:24:59.460
I'm not here to box.
I want the money.

307
00:24:59.460 --> 00:25:03.360
Calm down. I'll give you the money later.
Start!

308
00:25:22.460 --> 00:25:26.460
We have a new champion tonight.

309
00:25:26.460 --> 00:25:28.460
What's your name?

310
00:25:28.460 --> 00:25:30.460
Tim from Ban Nong Pradoo.

311
00:25:30.460 --> 00:25:32.360
Tim Pradoo Prew!

312
00:25:40.460 --> 00:25:44.360
Prize for the winner!

313
00:25:48.460 --> 00:25:51.460
I don't want it.
I only want my money bag. there.

314
00:25:51.460 --> 00:25:53.360
What an idiot!

315
00:26:03.460 --> 00:26:07.460
Hey! Hey! Why don't you take the prize
money? Why are you so stupid?

316
00:26:07.460 --> 00:26:09.460
Tell me if you want to fight again.

317
00:26:09.460 --> 00:26:11.460
You have the skill to win.

318
00:26:11.460 --> 00:26:15.460
I can see lots of money. lots and lots.

319
00:26:15.460 --> 00:26:17.460
You ask me to fight for money.

320
00:26:17.460 --> 00:26:19.460
Ai Hum Lae -

321
00:26:19.460 --> 00:26:21.460
why did you steal the villagers' money
to play gambling?

322
00:26:21.460 --> 00:26:23.460
For the investment...

323
00:26:23.460 --> 00:26:27.360
to get enough money
to help you find Ong Bak.

324
00:26:28.460 --> 00:26:32.460
You really want to help me?
Yes.

325
00:26:32.460 --> 00:26:35.460
This is Don's address.
Could you take me there?

326
00:26:35.460 --> 00:26:37.460
Keep it. I'll take you there later.

327
00:26:37.460 --> 00:26:39.460
Now could you give me some money.

328
00:26:39.460 --> 00:26:41.460
Give me. for the investment.

329
00:26:41.460 --> 00:26:42.460
When I make a profit.
I will pay you back.

330
00:26:42.460 --> 00:26:44.460
and I'll go anywhere you want.

331
00:26:44.460 --> 00:26:48.360
Absolutely sure!

332
00:26:51.460 --> 00:26:54.460
Go! Go away! Damn you!

333
00:26:54.460 --> 00:26:57.460
Peasant! Can't talk to you. stupid!

334
00:26:57.460 --> 00:26:59.460
Huh! Where will he sleep tonight?

335
00:26:59.460 --> 00:27:02.460
I don't care!
Or he can sleep with you!

336
00:27:02.460 --> 00:27:04.360
You're crazy!

337
00:27:06.460 --> 00:27:09.460
What shall I do?
Ai Keng will kill me.

338
00:27:09.460 --> 00:27:12.460
Muay! Take these drugs
to sell in Yai Lao's den.

339
00:27:12.460 --> 00:27:14.460
When we have enough money.
I will pay you back.

340
00:27:14.460 --> 00:27:16.460
I'm sure to earn money.
I know this place well.

341
00:27:16.460 --> 00:27:19.460
After the last one.
you still haven't learnt anything.

342
00:27:19.460 --> 00:27:23.460
I told you before.
I don't want to sell drugs.

343
00:27:23.460 --> 00:27:26.460
You must help me out.
I don't want to be hit again.

344
00:27:26.460 --> 00:27:28.460
OK?

345
00:27:28.460 --> 00:27:32.460
Yeah. Yeah... I will try.
but it'll have to be tomorrow.

346
00:27:32.460 --> 00:27:36.360
OK. now I feel much better.

347
00:27:42.460 --> 00:27:44.460
You don't have to look so happy.

348
00:27:44.460 --> 00:27:48.460
From the takings.
you'll get 30. but I'll get 70.

349
00:27:48.460 --> 00:27:50.460
Muay! 50/50.

350
00:27:50.460 --> 00:27:51.960
70/30.

351
00:27:51.960 --> 00:27:52.460
50/50.

352
00:27:52.460 --> 00:27:53.460
70/30.

353
00:28:26.460 --> 00:28:29.460
The money you asked
for starting your business in Bangkok

354
00:28:29.460 --> 00:28:31.460
I don't have it...

355
00:28:31.460 --> 00:28:35.460
because we had a very dry season.

356
00:28:35.460 --> 00:28:37.460
and Ong Bak's head was stolen by Ai Don.

357
00:28:37.460 --> 00:28:41.460
Dad wishes that you will help Bak Tim
to find and return Ong Bak to us...

358
00:28:41.460 --> 00:28:43.460
and save us from disaster.

359
00:28:43.460 --> 00:28:45.360
What nonsense!

360
00:29:13.460 --> 00:29:17.360
Warn! The pool is dry. Where are
we going to find drinking water?

361
00:29:22.460 --> 00:29:26.360
I pray to have Ong Bak
back with us soon. please.

362
00:29:33.460 --> 00:29:37.360
Ai Rung. are you alone?

363
00:29:38.460 --> 00:29:40.360
Ai Piew. are you betting?

364
00:29:41.460 --> 00:29:43.460
Brother I'm here.

365
00:29:43.460 --> 00:29:45.460
Damn Ai Yod.
Where have you been for months?

366
00:29:45.460 --> 00:29:47.460
I had to see my friends.

367
00:29:47.460 --> 00:29:49.460
You are fully aware
that I'm short of staff.

368
00:29:49.460 --> 00:29:51.460
You assist me first. hurry.

369
00:29:51.460 --> 00:29:53.460
Not now. I have to meet a friend.

370
00:29:53.460 --> 00:29:55.460
Don't make an excuse.
you help me now.

371
00:29:55.460 --> 00:29:56.460
Not today. some other day.

372
00:29:56.460 --> 00:29:58.460
No. now. quickly!

373
00:29:59.560 --> 00:30:01.460
Take it.

374
00:30:03.560 --> 00:30:05.460
Go away. you deal cards badly.

375
00:30:07.560 --> 00:30:09.560
Put down your bets now.

376
00:30:09.560 --> 00:30:13.460
At your age you should stay at home.
looking after your children

377
00:30:15.560 --> 00:30:17.560
What are you looking at? Get out!

378
00:30:17.560 --> 00:30:19.560
Go to that desk...

379
00:30:19.560 --> 00:30:21.560
and change your hair colour too.

380
00:30:21.560 --> 00:30:25.460
The colour that suits me.
and you have to copy.

381
00:30:27.560 --> 00:30:29.460
Put down your bets. to lose. to lose.

382
00:30:30.560 --> 00:30:33.560
Betting and losing is not my fault.

383
00:30:33.560 --> 00:30:35.560
Turn the cards.
19 and 19 both hands.

384
00:30:39.560 --> 00:30:41.560
Pay yje money.

385
00:30:41.560 --> 00:30:43.460
More bets down. bet. bet.

386
00:30:45.560 --> 00:30:46.560
Here's mine.

387
00:30:46.560 --> 00:30:47.560
Do you have money?

388
00:30:47.560 --> 00:30:49.560
Here it is - 3.000 real money.

389
00:30:49.560 --> 00:30:52.560
You want to play? You will lose...

390
00:30:52.560 --> 00:30:54.560
all your money and your belongings.

391
00:30:54.560 --> 00:30:58.560
I bet 200.
OK. 200.

392
00:30:58.560 --> 00:31:00.460
No card swapping.

393
00:31:01.560 --> 00:31:03.460
Oh! 18 points.

394
00:31:04.560 --> 00:31:12.060
Pay the money.
Wait... mine is 19. Pay me!

395
00:31:14.560 --> 00:31:16.460
This is 400.

396
00:31:21.560 --> 00:31:25.560
Ai has only 6 points. 1 card.
Mine is 9.

397
00:31:28.560 --> 00:31:33.060
8 points 3 cards.
9 points.

398
00:31:33.560 --> 00:31:35.560
What sort of cards are these?

399
00:31:37.560 --> 00:31:39.460
She's lucky.

400
00:31:40.560 --> 00:31:45.560
It's luck. good luck.
9 points.

401
00:31:47.560 --> 00:31:49.560
8 points again.
9 points again.

402
00:31:50.560 --> 00:31:54.460
Damn cards. take it.

403
00:31:56.560 --> 00:31:58.560
8 points again.

404
00:31:58.560 --> 00:32:02.460
Got you. pay!

405
00:32:03.560 --> 00:32:06.560
Damn! 8 points again.
9 to beat you.

406
00:32:08.560 --> 00:32:11.560
These cards are impossible.

407
00:32:11.560 --> 00:32:14.560
I must check if she is cheating.

408
00:32:17.560 --> 00:32:20.560
She got all 9 points for 15 games.
Took most of my money.

409
00:32:20.560 --> 00:32:22.460
Why do you pay her?

410
00:32:23.560 --> 00:32:27.560
I want to see if you will get 9 again.

411
00:32:27.560 --> 00:32:29.460
You're cheating me. bitch!

412
00:32:30.560 --> 00:32:34.460
I know I got 8
without turning the cards.

413
00:32:35.560 --> 00:32:37.560
Points? If 9...

414
00:32:37.560 --> 00:32:39.460
I'm certain that you cheat.

415
00:32:42.560 --> 00:32:45.560
Look! Loser! She got 4 points.

416
00:32:45.560 --> 00:32:46.560
I don't believe it.

417
00:32:47.560 --> 00:32:50.560
I'm sure that she concealed some cards.
I want to search her.

418
00:32:50.560 --> 00:32:52.560
Wait... Calm down!

419
00:32:53.560 --> 00:32:55.560
You should search her.

420
00:32:55.560 --> 00:32:56.560
Hey! Do you hide some cards?

421
00:32:56.560 --> 00:32:58.560
No. I don't.
Let's see.

422
00:32:58.560 --> 00:33:00.560
There are none. I told you.

423
00:33:00.560 --> 00:33:01.560
Any hidden in your bag?

424
00:33:01.560 --> 00:33:02.560
Let me check her myself.

425
00:33:02.560 --> 00:33:03.560
Don't trouble yourself.

426
00:33:03.560 --> 00:33:05.560
Come here.
OK you can go.

427
00:33:05.560 --> 00:33:06.560
You've got to search her everywhere.

428
00:33:06.560 --> 00:33:08.560
All done. everywhere.
You can go. go now.

429
00:33:08.560 --> 00:33:12.560
Don't come back here again. bitch!

430
00:33:12.560 --> 00:33:16.560
Winning every game like that
is bad for my place.

431
00:33:16.560 --> 00:33:18.560
Let's continue.
we can beat these people.

432
00:33:18.560 --> 00:33:20.560
No point to win. they're all broke.
Broke! Broke!

433
00:33:20.560 --> 00:33:22.560
She won all their money. nothing left.

434
00:33:22.560 --> 00:33:24.060
Don't you have a go at me.

435
00:33:24.060 --> 00:33:26.560
Total 8.000. I give your 3.000 back .

436
00:33:26.560 --> 00:33:28.560
Why is it only 3.000?

437
00:33:28.560 --> 00:33:30.560
You won't need so much anyway.

438
00:33:30.560 --> 00:33:32.560
What? No profit for me at all.

439
00:33:32.560 --> 00:33:34.560
Er... You take this money first.

440
00:33:34.560 --> 00:33:35.560
Don't spend too much.

441
00:33:35.560 --> 00:33:36.560
Give me another 1.000.

442
00:33:36.560 --> 00:33:38.560
3.000 is enough for you.

443
00:33:38.560 --> 00:33:40.560
This will merely cover my college fees.

444
00:33:40.560 --> 00:33:43.560
Hey! Seem to have a lot of money.

445
00:33:43.560 --> 00:33:45.460
That guy is here

446
00:33:46.560 --> 00:33:48.560
Lend me your money.

447
00:33:48.560 --> 00:33:50.560
This is my money.
Er... I'll pay you back.

448
00:33:50.560 --> 00:33:51.560
Will pay you back.

449
00:33:51.560 --> 00:33:55.560
Hi! I was on my way to pay you.
but you beat me to it. Here!

450
00:33:55.560 --> 00:33:56.560
That is my money.

451
00:33:56.560 --> 00:33:58.460
What?

452
00:34:00.560 --> 00:34:03.560
8.000 - I'll give you the rest later.

453
00:34:03.560 --> 00:34:06.560
Don't look at me so menacingly.

454
00:34:06.560 --> 00:34:08.560
I'm not bothered too much
about the rest of the money.

455
00:34:08.560 --> 00:34:12.460
but when you two try to cheat me.
I can't forget!

456
00:34:14.560 --> 00:34:18.460
Hold him! Beat him!
No. I won't fight you.

457
00:34:20.560 --> 00:34:22.460
Ai Tim!   Ai Tim!

458
00:34:24.560 --> 00:34:27.460
I won't fight. I won't fight.
Help! Help!

459
00:34:30.560 --> 00:34:33.560
You cheated me. here!

460
00:34:44.560 --> 00:34:45.560
You want trouble?

461
00:34:45.560 --> 00:34:47.460
Here's some!

462
00:34:57.560 --> 00:34:59.460
Will be seeing you!

463
00:35:02.560 --> 00:35:04.560
I have to thank you. Ai Tim.

464
00:35:04.560 --> 00:35:08.460
And I will help you to find Ong Bak

465
00:35:09.560 --> 00:35:13.560
Could you fight one more time?

466
00:35:13.560 --> 00:35:15.560
Wait... Listen to me first.

467
00:35:15.560 --> 00:35:18.560
You saw just a minute ago.
they beat me.

468
00:35:18.560 --> 00:35:20.560
If I don't pay them.
they will kill me.

469
00:35:20.560 --> 00:35:21.560
Could you help me?

470
00:35:21.560 --> 00:35:23.560
One last fight for me.

471
00:35:24.560 --> 00:35:27.560
OK. It doesn't matter anyway.
Stupid peasant!

472
00:35:27.560 --> 00:35:31.460
Stupid village. stupid villagers!
Relying on only one boxer...

473
00:35:32.560 --> 00:35:34.560
to find and return Ong Bak
to their village. Are you crazy?

474
00:35:34.560 --> 00:35:38.560
If Ong Bak is so powerful.
why let a thief cut his head off?

475
00:35:38.560 --> 00:35:41.460
It's only made from
pieces of stone and earth.

476
00:35:44.560 --> 00:35:46.560
Box me! Why box me?

477
00:35:46.560 --> 00:35:48.560
You are from the same village.
Don't kill each other.

478
00:35:48.560 --> 00:35:49.560
He boxed me!

479
00:35:49.560 --> 00:35:53.460
Never mind that! There! The people
you want to kill are over there!

480
00:35:54.560 --> 00:35:58.060
Ai Peng! Haven't you had enough?

481
00:35:58.060 --> 00:36:01.560
You want a kick to send you to sleep?.

482
00:36:03.560 --> 00:36:07.560
Umm... You have too many.

483
00:36:07.560 --> 00:36:11.460
Ai Yod. You know very well what to do.

484
00:36:13.560 --> 00:36:17.460
Muay. You know what to do.

485
00:36:18.560 --> 00:36:22.460
Use your individual skills.

486
00:36:25.560 --> 00:36:27.560
Don't leave me.

487
00:36:27.560 --> 00:36:29.460
After them!

488
00:36:41.560 --> 00:36:45.460
Follow them.
I'll go to block the other way.

489
00:36:54.560 --> 00:36:56.560
You!  I'm going!

490
00:37:20.560 --> 00:37:22.460
Get out. get out!

491
00:37:35.660 --> 00:37:37.560
Oh! How can he pass?

492
00:37:44.660 --> 00:37:48.560
Ooh! Is my bum still OK?
I don't know how I crossed them?

493
00:38:35.660 --> 00:38:37.660
Let me borrow the chopper quick.

494
00:38:37.660 --> 00:38:41.560
Come near me and I will slaughter you.

495
00:38:54.660 --> 00:38:58.560
Knives! Knives!
Big ones. small ones for sale.

496
00:39:34.660 --> 00:39:36.560
'Chilli Powder'

497
00:39:57.660 --> 00:39:59.560
Get him! Kill him!

498
00:41:25.660 --> 00:41:28.660
Ai Tim! Help me!

499
00:41:28.660 --> 00:41:30.660
I won't help.
You have to fight them yourself.

500
00:41:30.660 --> 00:41:34.660
Ai Don! Yes. I know his address.
I'll take you.

501
00:41:34.660 --> 00:41:38.560
Ai Tim! I know where Ai Don is.

502
00:42:01.660 --> 00:42:05.560
Who's next!

503
00:42:06.660 --> 00:42:08.660
I used to see Ai Don hanging
around here. selling drugs.

504
00:42:08.660 --> 00:42:12.660
Ask Muay. if you don't believe me...

505
00:42:12.660 --> 00:42:16.560
But today...

506
00:42:23.660 --> 00:42:27.560
That boy is here. Boss.

507
00:42:31.660 --> 00:42:35.660
Bring him here to fight
until the stakes are high.

508
00:42:35.660 --> 00:42:37.660
then I will get rid of him.

509
00:42:37.660 --> 00:42:41.560
Depends on how brave
you are to take a bet?

510
00:42:52.660 --> 00:42:54.560
You are a maniac!

511
00:43:19.660 --> 00:43:21.660
What's the matter. Yod?

512
00:43:21.660 --> 00:43:25.660
Ai Big Bear is challenging
Ai Tim to a fight.

513
00:43:58.660 --> 00:44:02.560
Come on! I'll fight you!
I'll teach you Thai boxing! Come on!

514
00:44:30.660 --> 00:44:32.660
Have you seen Bak Don?

515
00:44:32.660 --> 00:44:34.660
No. but I've seen a Thai man
being beaten.

516
00:44:34.660 --> 00:44:36.560
You are a coward.

517
00:44:46.660 --> 00:44:50.560
Are you going to help him?
Without help he'll die.

518
00:44:54.660 --> 00:44:57.560
Ai Tim!

519
00:45:00.760 --> 00:45:04.260
If I knew you were like this.
I wouldn't have helped you find Ong Bak

520
00:45:04.260 --> 00:45:08.660
Huh! You can do that later.
But now you must help him first.

521
00:45:49.260 --> 00:45:52.760
Lay down your stakes!
Lay down your stakes now!

522
00:45:52.760 --> 00:45:54.660
Lay down your stakes ... quickly.

523
00:45:54.760 --> 00:45:57.760
I'll give you 2 to 1. want to bet?

524
00:45:57.760 --> 00:46:00.760
OK. Put me down for three million.

525
00:46:11.760 --> 00:46:13.660
Attacking Enemy.

526
00:46:24.760 --> 00:46:26.660
Hanuman (monkey) crosses the city.

527
00:46:29.760 --> 00:46:33.760
If my man wins.
I want to collect the money.

528
00:46:33.760 --> 00:46:35.260
OK. I know!

529
00:46:35.260 --> 00:46:36.260
Thanks.

530
00:47:18.260 --> 00:47:21.760
Ai Tim! Ai Tim! The best!!!

531
00:47:22.260 --> 00:47:26.660
I think you've had enough. No chance
to win your money back today.

532
00:48:41.760 --> 00:48:45.760
Well done! Well done! The best!

533
00:48:45.760 --> 00:48:49.760
Muay. give me that.
No. Half then.

534
00:48:49.760 --> 00:48:53.660
I don't have to.
Trust me.

535
00:50:32.760 --> 00:50:36.760
Do you have any real contenders?

536
00:50:36.760 --> 00:50:38.760
Yes. but do you dare??

537
00:50:38.760 --> 00:50:40.660
Oh! No problem.

538
00:50:49.760 --> 00:50:53.660
Retreat!  Mother of God!

539
00:52:58.360 --> 00:53:00.860
Too much for you? Give up?

540
00:53:03.860 --> 00:53:06.360
Ay! Let go of me!

541
00:53:12.860 --> 00:53:14.860
Ay! Let me go!

542
00:53:51.860 --> 00:53:53.860
You've disappointed me.

543
00:54:22.860 --> 00:54:32.360
Good! The best! I told you. Muay.
to bet on him. We're rich! Rich!!

544
00:55:24.860 --> 00:55:26.860
Muay! Pick up the coins!

545
00:55:26.860 --> 00:55:31.360
Enough for today!
You won't get your money back.

546
00:55:34.360 --> 00:55:38.160
Ai Tim! You are so good. we have
a great opportunity to get rich.

547
00:55:38.160 --> 00:55:40.160
Brilliant!

548
00:55:41.060 --> 00:55:42.160
Ai Don!

549
00:55:45.060 --> 00:55:47.060
Follow them!

550
00:55:49.060 --> 00:55:50.960
Get them!

551
00:55:53.060 --> 00:55:56.960
Quick! Let's go!

552
00:55:59.060 --> 00:56:00.960
Ai Don!

553
00:56:05.060 --> 00:56:06.960
Follow them.

554
00:56:08.060 --> 00:56:10.060
This week I have to see customers.

555
00:56:10.060 --> 00:56:12.060
I want you to get things ready.

556
00:56:12.060 --> 00:56:15.060
Tell me first if there is a problem.

557
00:56:15.060 --> 00:56:17.060
Yes Boss.

558
00:56:17.060 --> 00:56:19.160
I want you to report everything.

559
00:56:21.160 --> 00:56:24.160
Ai Hum Lae!
Where will we find Ai Bak Don?

560
00:56:24.660 --> 00:56:26.660
You eat your food first. Eat!

561
00:56:27.060 --> 00:56:28.060
Don't worry.

562
00:56:28.060 --> 00:56:32.060
I'll find him! At the rice mill.
everyone know him well.

563
00:56:32.060 --> 00:56:34.060
Eat!

564
00:56:34.060 --> 00:56:37.060
Muay! Tomorrow you'll go with me.

565
00:56:37.060 --> 00:56:40.060
May be some chance to get money.

566
00:56:40.060 --> 00:56:42.060
I can't. Exams tomorrow.

567
00:56:42.060 --> 00:56:44.060
Exams!
I've never seen you attend class.

568
00:56:44.060 --> 00:56:47.960
How can you pass? Do you have
something special with the teacher?

569
00:56:48.660 --> 00:56:51.060
What!
A joke. a joke.

570
00:56:51.060 --> 00:56:54.960
You're a good student. you're clever.
Eat...

571
00:56:58.160 --> 00:57:01.060
Thanks a lot for helping me
to find Ong Bak.

572
00:57:02.060 --> 00:57:02.960
Don't thank me.

573
00:57:04.060 --> 00:57:07.060
Ai Yod. you own me 3 months rent.

574
00:57:07.060 --> 00:57:09.060
What are you going to do?

575
00:57:09.160 --> 00:57:11.060
Er... Give me 3 days.

576
00:57:12.060 --> 00:57:14.060
I'll pay you. This time for sure.

577
00:57:14.060 --> 00:57:16.060
You said 'sure' too many times already.

578
00:57:16.060 --> 00:57:19.060
I want money today -
otherwise you must move out.

579
00:57:20.060 --> 00:57:21.060
Will you accept this ring instead?

580
00:57:22.060 --> 00:57:23.060
OK

581
00:57:23.060 --> 00:57:27.060
You must pay the rent within 7 days.

582
00:57:27.060 --> 00:57:28.060
If you have no money again.

583
00:57:28.060 --> 00:57:31.960
I'll kick you out. understand?

584
00:58:00.660 --> 00:58:04.060
Son. I want you to return home
with Bak Tim.

585
00:58:04.060 --> 00:58:06.060
Don't worry
if you don't have enough money.

586
00:58:06.060 --> 00:58:09.060
I don't mind
if you don't want to become a monk.

587
00:58:09.060 --> 00:58:13.060
I only want you to visit us.

588
00:58:13.060 --> 00:58:14.960
I miss you. son.

589
00:59:03.060 --> 00:59:06.960
What's the matter! Am I not
as good as your ex-husband?

590
00:59:10.660 --> 00:59:11.960
You spoil my mood.

591
00:59:15.460 --> 00:59:17.360
Don!

592
00:59:18.060 --> 00:59:19.960
I don't want to sell drugs any more.

593
00:59:22.660 --> 00:59:23.960
Why?

594
00:59:31.660 --> 00:59:33.660
I want to stop.

595
00:59:40.660 --> 00:59:42.560
You want to stop?

596
00:59:45.060 --> 00:59:48.960
Really want to stop?
Come here!

597
00:59:50.060 --> 00:59:54.060
You think you can stop that easily.

598
00:59:54.060 --> 00:59:57.960
You think you can but you can't.

599
01:00:22.160 --> 01:00:24.060
Who?

600
01:00:34.160 --> 01:00:36.060
Huh! Ai Don.

601
01:00:42.760 --> 01:00:45.060
Pi Ngek. Pi Ngek. Pi Ngek. Pi Ngek.

602
01:00:47.760 --> 01:00:49.260
Where is Ong Bak?
I don't know.

603
01:00:49.160 --> 01:00:53.160
You brought it here!
I don't know.

604
01:00:53.160 --> 01:00:55.160
Ai Tim.

605
01:00:55.160 --> 01:00:57.060
Get away.

606
01:01:00.160 --> 01:01:02.060
Pi Ngek!

607
01:01:10.160 --> 01:01:14.060
Get out quickly. Don.

608
01:01:17.160 --> 01:01:19.060
Go. Go.

609
01:01:21.160 --> 01:01:24.260
Call an ambulance for Room 212.
She's dying. Urgent!

610
01:01:36.160 --> 01:01:40.060
Ai Tim! Come here quickly in a Tuk Tuk.

611
01:01:41.160 --> 01:01:43.060
Hurry up.

612
01:01:44.160 --> 01:01:46.060
You're dead.

613
01:02:43.160 --> 01:02:45.060
Keep following me!

614
01:03:04.160 --> 01:03:06.060
Come! You're dead.

615
01:03:18.160 --> 01:03:20.060
Huh! Ai Tim.

616
01:03:25.160 --> 01:03:29.060
Ai Tim! Brake!
Brake! Brake quickly!

617
01:03:32.160 --> 01:03:34.060
Oh Bhudda! Oh!

618
01:03:49.160 --> 01:03:51.160
Spread them out.

619
01:04:56.160 --> 01:04:58.060
Oh! Damn!

620
01:05:13.160 --> 01:05:16.060
Get out!

621
01:05:24.160 --> 01:05:25.260
You're dead.

622
01:06:20.160 --> 01:06:24.160
Remember! You must search every
square metre. Don't miss anything.

623
01:06:24.160 --> 01:06:28.060
Most important. you must not
allow any strangers in. Understand?

624
01:06:29.160 --> 01:06:31.060
Damn them!
They keep chasing after me.

625
01:08:31.260 --> 01:08:33.160
Get in.

626
01:08:36.260 --> 01:08:39.160
Today the Police and
National Heritage have found...

627
01:08:40.260 --> 01:08:43.260
lots of Buddha statues and relics
on the Chao Praya river's bank

628
01:08:43.260 --> 01:08:46.260
This finding of invaluable objects
is very significant.

629
01:08:46.260 --> 01:08:50.160
Because every piece
is a national treasure.

630
01:08:52.260 --> 01:08:56.360
National Heritage is making a catalogue
for protective conservation.

631
01:08:56.360 --> 01:09:01.160
We will report any developments
to this story.

632
01:09:11.260 --> 01:09:15.260
I told you not to cause trouble.

633
01:09:15.260 --> 01:09:19.160
I didn't.
They are looking for Ong Bak.

634
01:09:20.260 --> 01:09:22.160
What's Ong Bak?

635
01:09:23.260 --> 01:09:25.260
The head of the Buddha Statue
that I brought to you.

636
01:09:25.260 --> 01:09:29.260
Why does this man cause me
so much trouble?

637
01:09:29.260 --> 01:09:31.260
I lost my betting money.

638
01:09:31.260 --> 01:09:33.260
and all my relics collection...

639
01:09:33.260 --> 01:09:36.360
because of one peasant.

640
01:09:45.260 --> 01:09:49.160
I'm sorry I can't save her.

641
01:09:53.260 --> 01:09:55.160
Pi Ngek! Pi Ngek. Pi Ngek!

642
01:09:58.260 --> 01:10:02.260
Pi Ngek don't leave me.

643
01:10:02.260 --> 01:10:04.160
Who's she?

644
01:10:05.260 --> 01:10:07.260
Muay's big sister.

645
01:10:07.260 --> 01:10:11.160
You cann't leave me.
I have nobody.

646
01:10:17.260 --> 01:10:19.160
Muay. Muay.

647
01:10:24.260 --> 01:10:26.160
Ngek asked me to give this to you...

648
01:10:29.260 --> 01:10:31.260
'For Muay College Fees'

649
01:10:31.260 --> 01:10:33.160
I don't want it. don't want it

650
01:10:36.260 --> 01:10:40.260
I want you. I have nobody else.

651
01:10:40.260 --> 01:10:44.160
You can't leave. I've no one else.

652
01:10:45.260 --> 01:10:47.260
Don't be so sad. Muay.

653
01:10:47.260 --> 01:10:49.160
Birth and death are part of life.

654
01:10:50.260 --> 01:10:52.260
I won't leave you.

655
01:10:52.860 --> 01:10:56.260
What's this? What?

656
01:10:56.260 --> 01:10:58.260
Where are you taking me?

657
01:10:58.260 --> 01:11:02.160
Let's go. go quickly.
Go. go!

658
01:11:11.260 --> 01:11:14.260
Do you know who I am?

659
01:11:14.260 --> 01:11:16.160
How dare you attack my property!

660
01:11:17.260 --> 01:11:21.260
I don't know.
It's between Ai Tim and Ai Don.

661
01:11:21.260 --> 01:11:23.160
True! I don't know.

662
01:11:37.260 --> 01:11:41.160
I know that you are looking
for this Head.

663
01:11:42.260 --> 01:11:46.160
Do you really want it?

664
01:11:47.260 --> 01:11:51.160
If you want it.
I've a game for you to play.

665
01:11:58.260 --> 01:12:00.260
I saw Ong Bak with my own eyes.

666
01:12:00.260 --> 01:12:03.260
If you accept to fight for him.

667
01:12:03.260 --> 01:12:07.160
he will give you Ong Bak
and release Muay.

668
01:12:08.260 --> 01:12:12.160
What are you going to do?
Tell me.

669
01:12:14.260 --> 01:12:16.160
I will do anything...

670
01:12:18.260 --> 01:12:22.260
to bring back Ong Bak
to Ban Nong Pradoo.

671
01:12:22.260 --> 01:12:26.160
I'll sacrify even with my life.

672
01:12:43.360 --> 01:12:46.160
Why do you call me
to leave the frontier?

673
01:12:48.860 --> 01:12:56.160
To warn you to stay away from political
issues and I want you to make a bet.

674
01:12:57.160 --> 01:13:01.160
Oho.You want to revenge that
country boxer to death!

675
01:13:01.860 --> 01:13:04.160
How much you want to bet? Your call.

676
01:13:05.860 --> 01:13:07.860
You don't call the shots anymore!

677
01:14:02.260 --> 01:14:07.160
On the East corner is a Thai Boxer.
He's new to us .

678
01:14:10.260 --> 01:14:16.160
The Burmese Boxer is on the West
corner. He's one of the best.

679
01:14:18.260 --> 01:14:26.160
Now the fight has begun.
(Voice of the commentator continues)

680
01:16:08.460 --> 01:16:12.960
Ai Tim!  Ai Tim! Are you OK?
Enough.

681
01:16:52.460 --> 01:16:55.260
Hey! If you want Ong Bak. follow me.

682
01:17:24.460 --> 01:17:29.460
You're crooks too. Tim lost
the fight so I could win the bet.

683
01:17:39.460 --> 01:17:40.460
Huh! This is Pra.

684
01:17:41.460 --> 01:17:45.460
It's just the head of some worthless
statue that you're trying to get.

685
01:17:46.460 --> 01:17:51.060
I'm not interested in the head.
I just want you to box for me.

686
01:17:51.460 --> 01:17:57.460
Don't dare challenge me because
I can make you live or die.

687
01:17:59.660 --> 01:18:02.460
Damn you! You betray us.

688
01:18:03.460 --> 01:18:06.460
Ai Tim lost the fight for you.
why don't you return the head to him?

689
01:18:06.960 --> 01:18:09.060
Son of a bitch!

690
01:18:13.960 --> 01:18:18.060
Calm down.
Finish them after I've gone.

691
01:18:19.460 --> 01:18:26.960
You got hurt but I got the money.
Remember that I ordered this.

692
01:18:28.060 --> 01:18:31.060
Get rid of them.
I can't help if they don't listen.

693
01:18:47.460 --> 01:18:48.960
Huh! Kill them!

694
01:19:00.460 --> 01:19:01.460
Pi Yod!

695
01:19:03.460 --> 01:19:06.460
Damn!
I told him not to make a noise.

696
01:19:20.460 --> 01:19:23.460
Hey! Do it quickly!
Police may be here soon.

697
01:19:31.960 --> 01:19:34.060
Hey! Go there.

698
01:21:25.160 --> 01:21:27.060
Where is Ong Bak?

699
01:21:42.460 --> 01:21:48.060
Hey! I go with you.
No. I can't let anyone die for Ong Bak.

700
01:21:48.460 --> 01:21:51.060
Except me. only me.

701
01:21:56.960 --> 01:22:00.060
Ai Tim. Ai Tim.

702
01:22:02.460 --> 01:22:04.460
Let me help you.

703
01:22:06.960 --> 01:22:11.760
I don't want to be like this.
I apologise to you.

704
01:22:11.960 --> 01:22:15.060
Let me do one good deed
for Ban Nong Pradoo.

705
01:22:16.460 --> 01:22:19.960
At least...
Let me start the bike for you.

706
01:22:22.560 --> 01:22:27.460
I. Bak Hum Lae.
from Ban Nong Pradoo.

707
01:22:38.560 --> 01:22:44.260
Don told me there is a secret cave
behind the next mountain.

708
01:26:23.060 --> 01:26:25.060
Still not dead!

709
01:26:32.560 --> 01:26:36.060
You want Ong Bak! You have to
exchange it with your life.

710
01:26:36.560 --> 01:26:38.560
We're cutting the biggest head.

711
01:28:16.760 --> 01:28:21.360
Ai Tim!  Ai Tim.....Ai Ti...

712
01:29:33.560 --> 01:29:36.560
Ai Ham Lae!  Are you OK?

713
01:29:42.560 --> 01:29:46.560
Go and get Ong Bak. Go!

714
01:29:48.060 --> 01:29:50.060
Don't worry about me.
Go and get Ong Bak.

715
01:29:50.460 --> 01:29:51.560
Go!

716
01:30:55.060 --> 01:31:01.660
Huh! Where're you running to?
Continue working! Cut the head off!

717
01:31:10.160 --> 01:31:13.660
Be careful!
Last time I told him to lose.

718
01:32:23.160 --> 01:32:28.260
The head is off now boss.
Good. pull it off.

719
01:34:20.160 --> 01:34:22.260
Die..e..e...

720
01:36:09.660 --> 01:36:15.260
You want this head!
I want to see if it's unbreakable.

721
01:37:36.160 --> 01:37:37.160
Ai Hum Lae!

722
01:37:39.260 --> 01:37:42.360
Ai Hum Lae... Are you hurt?

723
01:37:44.960 --> 01:37:51.760
Take... take... Ong Bak
back to our... our village.

724
01:37:53.760 --> 01:37:56.360
Ai Pi Yod!  Ai Pi Yod!
What's happenning?

725
01:37:59.760 --> 01:38:00.960
Ai Hum Lae.

726
01:38:00.960 --> 01:38:16.260
Muay.. finish.. your studying
and find.. a good job.

727
01:38:20.760 --> 01:38:30.760
Bak Tim..Tell my dad
I can't become a monk.

728
01:38:30.760 --> 01:38:36.260
Huh! What are you saying? Let's go
to hospital and you will be fine. Pi Yod.

729
01:38:36.260 --> 01:38:40.760
Ai Hum Lae.
Ai Pi Yod. Ai Pi Yod. Huh!

730
01:38:41.760 --> 01:38:47.360
You can't die! You promised
not to leave me. you can't die.

731
01:38:47.360 --> 01:38:53.360
You can't do this! You mustn't
lie to me. you cannot lie to me.

732
01:38:53.760 --> 01:38:58.760
Do you understand! You promised me!
I've nobody else! I've nobody else!

733
01:38:58.760 --> 01:39:05.060
Wake up now! Don't do this to me.
you can't. can't. Understand!

734
01:39:05.060 --> 01:39:11.360
Wake up now! Ai Pi Yod. you can't die.
You must keep your promise.

735
01:39:15.760 --> 01:39:39.760
(Weeping goes on continuously)
